jener strengt tatt prisen for beste film. Som beste film om en sylskarp, rar engelskmann, spilt av en blendende britisk skuespiller i 30-\u00e5ra med privatskolebakgrunn stiller de omtrent likt."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "93bd12cd0e6953a9fdcaf44dbd82027b564cabc52bdb8259bfbaa7e0bd34a7f8"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-04T08:04:28.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Filmen om Steven Hawking er bedre spilt enn tenkt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article10615522.ece/3hfabk/ALTERNATES/w980-default/TheTeoryOfbild.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5918ccc3fab0f13852b240853c826b68b67b9226.jpg?59469ca0"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "P\u00e5 hjul med Hawking -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "5918ccc3fab0f13852b240853c826b68b67b9226"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["anmeldelser", "det skjer", "film", "musikk", "tv", "museum", "scene", "spill"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "anmeldelser,det skjer,film,musikk,tv,museum,scene,spill"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "film"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["the imitation game", "oscar", "hawing", "the theory of everything", "jane"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["felicity jones", "james marsh", "morten tyldums", "eddie redmayne", "steven hawking"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article10615522.ece/3hfabk/ALTERNATES/w980-default/TheTeoryOfbild.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "